snippet.title: Building Beautiful Burgers! - VR The Diner Duo Gameplay - Co-op VR Experience (HTC VIVE)
snippet.description:
Welcome to my VR Diner Duo Gameplay! Vr Diner Duo is a multiplayer virtual reality game where the chef experiences the game in VR and the waitress can play the game just like a normal video game without the use of a VR device. This make for some very interesting and sometimes dangerous co-op VR gameplay. I hope you enjoyed this episode of VR The Diner Duo, thanks for watching and liking.

My Waitress
Diaexx: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXIjiWikYfQm1OkEIwfVJgA

☆Merch: http://draegast.fanfiber.com/
☆2nd Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCj8su0fXs_NCkUsn7Xm9N2Q

You are a chef in VR who need to satisfy your customers in a limited amount of time. Share the experience with a friend in local multiplayer mode. Chaotic levels are waiting for you!

VR The Diner Duo on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/530120/

☆Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DraegastYoutube
☆Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/draegastyt
☆Twitter: https://twitter.com/Draegast
☆Discord: https://discord.gg/0136qg4dtRxtL6jZE

Intro: Title: Richard Caddock, WRLD, Nitro Fun, Slips & Slurs & Subtact - Break The Silence
Listen on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/5l33DXPACHY0SY8Eolk1wI
Video Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aUGA-RJoqNA

Outro: JAWN - Duck of Doom https://soundcloud.com/jawnmusic/duck-of-doom
